    <step order="5" name="Author Response DTO">`WorkspaceStateResponse` record with `tabs`, `activeTabId`, `userSelection`.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Tests">Add endpoint integration test in `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Api/Workspace/`: 401 unauth, 403 tenant mismatch, 200 happy path with tabs, 200 empty.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Publish-Size Verification">dotnet publish; record delta.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL)">code-review + adr-check (ADR-008/010/013/014/016/029).</step>
